  Description: Having faced countless foes and the chaos of battle, you have learned
    how to stand strong in the face of fear. Your proficiency rank for Will saves
    increases to expert. When you roll a success at a Will save against a fear effect,
    you get a critical success instead. In addition, anytime you gain the frightened
    condition, reduce its value by 1.
